Package farm.gui

Class ApplicationManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • farm.gui.ApplicationManager
  • public class ApplicationManager
extends java.lang.Object
    The ApplicationManager class manages the order of execution of GUI windows. It instantiates the game environment and runs game until completion, passing the state of the game between windows.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Megan Steenkamp
